Usage: get_socv_reporting_nsigma_multiplier [-help] -view <viewName> {[-setup | -hold ]}

-help                # Prints out the command usage
-hold                # Get the sigma multiplier for hold mode (bool, optional)
-setup               # Get the sigma multiplier for setup mode (bool, optional)
-view <viewName>     # Get the sigma multiplier value for specified view
                     # (string, required)